description: Department of Elections - Elected Mr. Wasala Mudiyanselage Wala Gedara Janaka Bandara as a member of the Dimbulagala Pradeshiya Sabha and Mr. Suraweera Arachchilage Bandula Samansiri as Chairman of the Lankapura Pradeshiya Sabha - Vacating the office of member of the Thalawa Pradeshiya Sabha by Mr. Dissanayaka Mudiyanselage Sarath Dissanayaka
